DOC.brief_summary: Induction of labor is performed via the vaginal misorostol 25 ug/ 6 hours and intracervical foley's cather administration and both techniques performed together.
DOC.brief_title: Combined Method for Induction of Labor
DOC.criteria: females presenting for induction of labor previous cesarean section previous uterine scars e.g. myomectomy refusal to participate in the study
